(7, 'Lawyer & Lawyer Assistant Needed', '<p>We are hiring for Lawyer and Lawyer Assistant. Join our team! you will acquire&nbsp;such broad experience in the biggest law firm in West Sumatera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><u>Lawyer Qualification:</u></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Male / Female</li>\r\n	<li>Law School/Faculty Graduate (Min. S1)</li>\r\n	<li>Aged within 25 and 30 years old</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum GPA: 2.75</li>\r\n	<li>Already sworn as a Lawyer by the High Court</li>\r\n	<li>able to work as a team</li>\r\n	<li>able to communicate well</li>\r\n	<li>able to write legal document draft</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><u>Lawyer Assitant Qualification:</u></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Male / Female</li>\r\n	<li>Law School/Faculty Graduate (Min. S1)</li>\r\n	<li>Aged within 18 and 25 years old</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum GPA: 2.75</li>\r\n	<li>Already have PKPA certificate</li>\r\n	<li>able to work as a team</li>\r\n	<li>able to communicate well</li>\r\n	<li>able to write legal document draft</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>For those who are interested and meet the requirement, please submit your:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Curriculum Vitae with 1 copy latest photograph</li>\r\n	<li>a copy of Graduate Certificate and Academic Transcript</li>\r\n	<li>a copy of PKPA certificate</li>\r\n	<li>a copy of PERADI Card</li>\r\n	<li>an essay about Litigation/Business Law/Government Law&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Other supportive documents</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>to Miko Kamal &amp; Associates (MKA) Office at</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Anggrek Building 1nd Floor, Jl. Permindo No. 61, Padang - 25111</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Due at Friday, January 21st, 2022</p>\r\n', 'Lawyer', '20220113152025MKA Job Vacancy.jpg', 'lawyer--lawyer-assistant-needed', '2019-06-14');
