(3, 21, 'Kunjungan 2', 'Kunjungan 3', '<p>\r\nMr\r\n Supono (our client) was aggrieved by PT. LAB, PT. AG and BPKPBPBB (The \r\ndefendants). According to the unlawful act, The High Court has punished \r\nthe defendants to pay the costs in the sum of IDR 3.5 Billion. \r\nFurthermore the verdict was also strengthen by the High Court of \r\nPekanbaru dated on January 16, 2018. &nbsp;So the defendants filed an appeal \r\nto the Supreme Court. With good communication skills and measurable \r\nnegotiations, a peace agreement was finally reached between the client \r\nand the Defendants before the case was decided by the Supreme Court of \r\nthe Republic of Indonesia.\r\n\r\n<br></p>', '<p>\r\nMr\r\n Supono (our client) was aggrieved by PT. LAB, PT. AG and BPKPBPBB (The \r\ndefendants). According to the unlawful act, The High Court has punished \r\nthe defendants to pay the costs in the sum of IDR 3.5 Billion. \r\nFurthermore the verdict was also strengthen by the High Court of \r\nPekanbaru dated on January 16, 2018. &nbsp;So the defendants filed an appeal \r\nto the Supreme Court. With good communication skills and measurable \r\nnegotiations, a peace agreement was finally reached between the client \r\nand the Defendants before the case was decided by the Supreme Court of \r\nthe Republic of Indonesia.\r\n\r\n<br></p>', '2018-10-01', ''),
